{"tid":1141233,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟被背叛痛啲定遺憾/錯過痛啲？","createTime":"2019-05-06T10:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T14:53:28.000Z","uid":46480,"like":15,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c33b70580defb75cc90710a37260fe095b6bfb8e","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"兩隻都試過<br />\n被背叛果次唔知係咪因為感情唔太深<br />\n同埋自己有個肯定既原因比自己去放手忘記<br />\n時間一過好快無乜事<br />\n<br />\n但係遺憾/錯過就仆街啦<br />\n都唔知自己做乜鳩<br />\n錯過左，可能係自己果刻sense唔到<br />\n或者係果刻有其他原因逼自己拒絕<br />\non99回頭先發現<br />\n其實根本忘記唔到<br />\n人地又無做錯啲咩<br />\n連想諗佢係衰人比自己容易啲忘記都唔得<br />\n仲要果種拿住拿住既感覺係隨時間增長<br />\n不斷諗如果果日做左另一個選擇<br />\n今日會唔會已經一齊左而唔係變成陌生人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被背叛痛啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遺憾/錯過痛啲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XksPxZirnTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXksPxZirnTA&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=afc2fea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XksPxZirnTA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LfGj3epxFd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLfGj3epxFd8&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2cc817da\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LfGj3epxFd8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LfGj3epxFd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLfGj3epxFd8&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2cc817da\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LfGj3epxFd8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vsBf_0gDxSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvsBf_0gDxSM&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=23ec9e25\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vsBf_0gDxSM</a>"},{"pid":"405648e4511d323755072b7a3dbc4f24c02a63bf","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"仲有首應該係呢個<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YEUeiKuvYes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYEUeiKuvYes&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=67e2f0ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YEUeiKuvYes</a>"},{"pid":"d410052ae539a987bc0db75e4a3a221de42c757f","tid":1141233,"uid":9815,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"一定係錯過<br />\n連放低嘅原因都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d7460775cc477d361130f4d071202cc803b436","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d410052ae539a987bc0db75e4a3a221de42c757f","tid":1141233,"uid":9815,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"一定係錯過<br />\n連放低嘅原因都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"exact7ly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad0e40c64d640f54aa2e5883697a396231f2f96","tid":1141233,"uid":251404,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"如果俾人背叛嘅話 起碼都可以有個理由去憎佢 知道呢個人唔值得 俾自己放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但錯過嘅話 你會一直都記得呢個得唔到嘅人 同佢嘅回憶只可以回味 一諗起呢度就覺得好心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfdaa5dae4b643c70b38e659bfec7ff79460841","tid":1141233,"uid":55162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"背叛痛d<br />\n因為係未做到想做嘅野先會遺憾<br />\n做咗結果唔一定係好<br />\n但背叛係個已經存在嘅結果<br />\n痛得好真實"},{"pid":"a580b5e34d86c3fc1b0f5710946d4a3c8739003a","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cfdaa5dae4b643c70b38e659bfec7ff79460841","tid":1141233,"uid":55162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"背叛痛d<br />\n因為係未做到想做嘅野先會遺憾<br />\n做咗結果唔一定係好<br />\n但背叛係個已經存在嘅結果<br />\n痛得好真實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"但已知結果先有理由去放低<br />\n唔知結果放低唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb2dad707f453b68fb8a6a9018463b34bd8b4ac","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4907868469d259d1bd57aab17ed76e0dc2c958","tid":1141233,"uid":41009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"被背叛會憎佢<br />\n佢犯過呢個錯就唔會再信佢<br />\n<br />\n但錯過會成日諗<br />\n如果冇錯過會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fe38148cf3e768672fd067171975e0cdf694c5","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4907868469d259d1bd57aab17ed76e0dc2c958","tid":1141233,"uid":41009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"被背叛會憎佢<br />\n佢犯過呢個錯就唔會再信佢<br />\n<br />\n但錯過會成日諗<br />\n如果冇錯過會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"絲打你最後揀左你鐘意份工，無搬到過去？"},{"pid":"b5353489a25748a315c1b5edf5dfe6a3a21847fe","tid":1141233,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17fe38148cf3e768672fd067171975e0cdf694c5","tid":1141233,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4907868469d259d1bd57aab17ed76e0dc2c958","tid":1141233,"uid":41009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"被背叛會憎佢<br />\n佢犯過呢個錯就唔會再信佢<br />\n<br />\n但錯過會成日諗<br />\n如果冇錯過會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"絲打你最後揀左你鐘意份工，無搬到過去？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:37:56.000Z","msg":"冇搬呀<br />\n而家個關係其實我都唔知算點<br />\n佢會過